{
  "title": "Taaciladhane ki Ngudradrekay",
  "titleCh": "魯凱族的水源地圖",
  "soundPath": null,
  "sentence": [
    {
      "chinese": "魯凱族的居住區域非常廣，多高山，多林，水源豐富而成溪流、成河川、成瀑布、成沼澤地和濕地。魯凱族靠水源而居，方便取生活用水，與耕作田地；可捉蝦\\、洗衣、洗澡。就算是枯水期，仍有水源可取水。族人非常的敬重水源，以免招致報復性的災損，努力的持守護山護水的責任。",
      "ab": "Kay taitalikayyane ki Ngudradrekay kay kadaengane, suaadraw makalra abelenge ku lregelrege, makalra ku angatungatu ku mualualualudru ku acilay, adrakeakerale, adrakerale, avaalru, kaadravane, latuuturu, ilrici si tategavane. Wasilape ku apakaduadhane mualru ku acilay ku saagane, tamuane tukaange, kiapase, tasinasinavane si taubanabanavane, adravane lukakalakusilane, yakayyana ku tamuane malra ku acilay. Muasakene turamuru amanilu kiubilrilaku ngitatulisita, amia kakalithi palakebe ki sanakataaciladhane ki valruaalru ki kadaengane.",
      "order": "1",
