    {
      "chinese": "河川發源自「安靜湖（小鬼湖）」， 經大武、東川；另一條是發源自「北大武山」和「團結山」，每一支溪流都有專屬名字。以溪流為部落和族群的自然界線，大頭目也以河川山嶺為獵區及接受納貢的範圍。",
      "ab": "Ku kaadravane amani kay singikay Taidrengere ngukakay Labuane, Talamakaw, lakamani kikay singikay Tagarawsu si Parathudane ku takaabelengane ki lregelrege. Yakay ku lanagane ki aciacilay ki drakerale, arakay ki vaalru ki kaadravane maagisi ki badha, arakay kay talialaalay maagiagisi ku talikay lini ku takadrengane si kisualupu ku nimalrane ku singikay ki aciacilay.",
